  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested a premium photography website featuring their original photos with style analysis and feedback functionality. The conversation stalled when no photos were provided despite detailed requirements. Manus correctly identified the missing dependency and requested the images before proceeding.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser wants a professional photography portfolio website with automated style analysis and critique features\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nRequirements gathering and dependency identification for missing photo assets\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [requirement_clarification] Photo Upload Request — Clear request for missing photo assets needed to proceed\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Wait for photo assets before starting development\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Clear requirement specification\n- Proper dependency checking\nFailed / suboptimal:\n\n- User did not provide required assets\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Complex web project requires actual content before development\n\n## Challenges & Blockers\n\n- Missing photo assets required for analysis and gallery creation\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- What specific photos will be analyzed?\n- What photographic styles are represented?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Wait for photo uploads\n- Begin style analysis once images are provided\n- Develop premium gallery interface\n---\nUID: qmXNu7Ov2IYJsScj8MASuO | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0095\n"
